类 Map

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class Map
extends javafx.scene.Parent
    This class records map information, such as images,coordinates, and current status of the map
    Function:
    provide a basis for judging functions such as car driving logic and piece adsorption. The map information needs to be reset during initialization. When the puzzle is placed on the map, the map information changes.
